        "name": "Precious Gleam",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "text": "**Sin:** greed  \n  \nYou temporarily enhance a weapon, replacing it with finer materials. On the next successful attack with that weapon during the spell\u2019s duration, the attack deals an additional 1d6 precision damage. You can choose for the metal to become your choice of cold iron, silver, or steel, causing the attack to bypass resistances accordingly.",
